data.actual_result: The message does not copy, and thus when you try to paste it, it is blank/pasted nothing
data.expected_result: Contents of the rich embed message should paste in the channel after copying
data.short_description: Unable to copy text from rich embedded messages
data.steps_to_repro: - Have a bot send you a rich embed message - Press and hold on the message - Press “Copy Text” - Try and paste the message in a channel
